headline: Invesco Canada announces cash distributions for its ETFs
summary: Invesco Canada Ltd. ("Invesco") announced today the May 2025 distributions for its exchange-traded funds (ETFs). Unitholders of record on May 29, 2025, will receive cash distributions payable on June 6, 2025.
